{"tid":919373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西班牙官員稱　不會與中國簽署「一帶一路」倡議","createTime":"2018-11-28T03:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T10:17:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5a00cd40f16ad42d1647880f2f5d25585717267e","tid":919373,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T03:55:40.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平抵達西班牙首都馬德里，開始對西班牙進行國事訪問。習近平在西班牙報章發表署名文章，呼籲共建「一帶一路」倡議，西班牙發展戰略對接，實現互利共贏。<br />\n<br />\n不過，西班牙首相府一名官員表示，西班牙不會簽署加入「一帶一路」倡議，這名官員表示，歐洲與亞洲一直存在連繫，歐洲國家應該按現行的框架工作。歐盟在九月份已經公布有連繫亞洲的計劃。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1430496-20181128.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1430496-20181128.htm&d=uNoWp92JVkE6MadDRBf1OLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=a9e39e60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1430496-20181128.htm&h=51806cd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1430496-20181128.htm</a>"},{"pid":"70af429fadab39d95dd226df984e245b7f70402e","tid":919373,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T03:57:14.000Z","msg":"反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89a7072b69048d9600046da7d38a3a73a79c05f","tid":919373,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T03:57:38.000Z","msg":"御駕親征都冇面俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11fdacc9caa4c8a7906c41533df932d9fa18d84","tid":919373,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T09:49:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1d384242d38e941f1ab8d03bcb7096b20ab5a0","tid":919373,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c89a7072b69048d9600046da7d38a3a73a79c05f","tid":919373,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyT